<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="excuse-n">excuse <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'skjuːs/    美 /ɪk'skjuːs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 借口；理由：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stop <strong>making excuses for</strong> being lazy! 
别再为你的懒惰找借口了！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Birthdays are always a good <strong>excuse for</strong> a party. 
生日总是聚会的好理由。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I'm sorry I stepped outside for a smoke. I was very tired.
— There is no excuse <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ this while you are on duty.  （2003 北京改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>